719
01:14:35,811 --> 01:14:39,968
- Hand him over.
<i>- No, no, get off of me.</i>

720
01:14:41,270 --> 01:14:43,850
- It was me. You’re right, it was me.
- It’s too late.

721
01:14:43,952 --> 01:14:45,487
- Now, give me the doll.
- No.

722
01:14:45,570 --> 01:14:47,548
<i>- Greta?</i>
- Now! I’m not joking around!

723
01:14:48,348 --> 01:14:50,435
Get your things and
get out of here.

724
01:14:50,936 --> 01:14:54,160
You know, everyone just seems to
be in a big hurry for me to leave.

725
01:14:54,162 --> 01:14:55,439
- You’re right?
- Yeah.

726
01:14:55,441 --> 01:14:58,456
Maybe... Maybe you left
that little message for me.

727
01:14:59,394 --> 01:15:01,211
Or are you gonna say
it was the doll too?

728
01:15:01,212 --> 01:15:02,928
- What did Brahms do?
- Cole,

729
01:15:03,117 --> 01:15:05,139
you don’t understand what’s happening.
The doll...

730
01:15:05,141 --> 01:15:07,550
No. I think I understand
exactly what’s going on.

731
01:15:07,552 --> 01:15:08,320
Give me the doll!

732
01:15:08,321 --> 01:15:09,864
- What’s so special about this doll?
- Cole!

733
01:15:10,329 --> 01:15:11,499
Cole, please.

734
01:15:11,824 --> 01:15:12,906
No!

735
01:15:13,430 --> 01:15:14,591
Cole!

736
01:15:15,091 --> 01:15:16,162
Fine.

